in the online dating industry, and won multiple awards for his work. He has on Channel 4 News, the BBC and \u003ci\u003eThe\u003c/i\u003e \u003ci\u003eSunday Times\u003c/i\u003e, among others. His podcast \u003ci\u003eThe Dark Web\u003c/i\u003e was an immediate top-ten hit on Audible and his latest podcast, \u003ci\u003eThe Lazarus Heist\u003c/i\u003e which he co-hosted with Jean Lee for the BBC World Service, was number one in the UK Apple chart.","seoFriendlyUrl":"/authors/290042/geoff-white","sequence":1,"role":{"code":"2","description":"Author","seq":1,"primaryFlag":true},"isVarious":false}],"textTypes":{"8":{"textTypeId":8,"textTypeDesc":"Biography","text":[{"text":"\u003cb\u003eGeoff White \u003c/b\u003eis an investigative journalist and acclaimed podcaster, covering technology and organised crime. He has reported on the Snowden leaks, investigated the hacking of Britain's largest internet service provider TalkTalk, exposed fraud in the online dating industry, and won multiple awards for his work. He has on Channel 4 News, the BBC and \u003ci\u003eThe\u003c/i\u003e \u003ci\u003eSunday Times\u003c/i\u003e, among others. His podcast \u003ci\u003eThe Dark Web\u003c/i\u003e was an immediate top-ten hit on Audible and his latest podcast, \u003ci\u003eThe Lazarus Heist\u003c/i\u003e which he co-hosted with Jean Lee for the BBC World Service, was number one in the UK Apple chart.","sequence":1,"textSource":null,"textAuthor":null}]},"9":{"textTypeId":9,"textTypeDesc":"Synopsis","text":[{"text":"They have been accused of causing mayhem in Hollywood with the infamous Sony hack.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nThey're allegedly behind WannaCry, a cyber-attack that brought NHS hospitals to a dangerous standstill.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nAnd it has been claimed that they have stolen more than $1 billion in an international crime spree.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nThey are the Lazarus Group, a shadowy cabal of hackers accused of working on behalf of the North Korean state. North Korea denies the allegations, saying the accusations are American attempts to tarnish its image. \u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nFrom the streets of Dhaka to the casinos of Macau to the secretive capital of Pyongyang, this shocking story uncovers the secret world of the Lazarus Group, their victims and those who have tried - and so far failed - to stop them.","sequence":1,"textSource":null,"textAuthor":null}]},"21":{"textTypeId":21,"textTypeDesc":"Reviews","text":[{"text":"\u003cb\u003ePacy and eye-popping. It's chilling to read how easily dictators blessed with talented hackers can now terrorise democracies\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":1,"textSource":"author of Kleptopia","textAuthor":"Tom Burgis"},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eThis is a mindbending investigation. You'll never see North Korea the same way again\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":2,"textSource":"Sunday Times bestselling author of Moneyland and Butler to the World","textAuthor":"Oliver Bullough"},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eOne of the most incredible cyber-espionage stories I've ever heard\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":3,"textSource":"author of The Missing Crypto Queen","textAuthor":"Jamie Bartlett"},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eCyber warfare and criminal hacking has never been more pertinent. This a must read to understand the threats currently facing all of us globally\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":4,"textSource":"Annie Machon, author of Spies, Lies and Whistleblowers","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003ePart detective story, part thriller, but scary since it is all true. White exposes North Korea as a pariah State where ruthless dictatorship joins forces with international cyber crime. A compelling account of a 21st century threat to us all\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":5,"textSource":"Sir David Omand, former head of GCHQ and author of How Spies Think","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eGeoff White's thorough investigation reads as part detective story, part thriller, but scary since it is all true. He exposes North Korea as a pariah State where ruthless dictatorship joins forces with international cyber crime. A compelling account of a 21st century threat to us all\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":6,"textSource":"Professor Sir David Omand, former head of GCHQ and author of How Spies Think","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eNorth Korea is one of the world's least understood countries. By uncovering key details about the innovative methods of the Lazarus Group, and richly detailing its operations, Geoff White has performed a crucial service in our conception of the criminal state that is North Korea. Read this book!\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":7,"textSource":"Isaac Stone Fish, author of America Second: How America's Elites Are Making China Stronger","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eIn this captivating gem of a book, Geoff takes us on a whirlwind global adventure that covers the events around a fascinating and important cyber attack that we all should be aware of\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":8,"textSource":"Jack Rhysider, founder of Darknet Diaries","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eWhile the book reads like a typical Hollywood crime drama, in the end the good guys do not win\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":9,"textSource":"Foreign Policy","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eA pacey insight into the cutting edge of modern crime and an equally fascinating portrait of life inside North Korea \u003c/b\u003e","sequence":10,"textSource":"The Economist","textAuthor":null},{"text":"A globe-trotting, criminal thriller, with geopolitical implications, glitz and glamour, high tech, life and death stakes, and, what's more-it is all true.","sequence":11,"textSource":"Diplomatic Courier","textAuthor":"Joshua C. Huminsk"},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eA riveting investigation reveals a world of shadowy criminals, sophisticated hacks and bungled schemes\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":12,"textSource":"Financial Times","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eA captivating read that contains everything from geopolitics and cybercrime to Hollywood and the idiosyncrasies of North Korea's over-the-top regime-none of which can be dull on any day\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":13,"textSource":"India Times","textAuthor":null},{"text":"\u003cb\u003eAn easy-to-read book on cybersecurity. If you hold crypto, you need to know the basics of security\u003c/b\u003e","sequence":14,"textSource":"CEO of Binance","textAuthor":"Changpeng Zhao"}]},"200":{"textTypeId":200,"textTypeDesc":"ONIX Description","text":[{"text":"\u003cb\u003eBASED ON THE NO 1 HIT PODCAST 'The Lazarus Heist'\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e'You'll never see North Korea the same way again' \u003c/b\u003eOliver Bullough, author of \u003ci\u003eMoneyland\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e'One of the most incredible cyber-espionage stories I've ever heard' \u003c/b\u003eJamie Bartlett, author of \u003ci\u003eThe Missing Crypto Queen\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e'Pacy and eye-popping'\u003c/b\u003e - Tom Burgis, author of \u003ci\u003eKleptopia\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nThey have been accused of causing mayhem in Hollywood with 2014's infamous Sony hack.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nThey're allegedly behind WannaCry, a cyber-attack which brought NHS hospitals to a dangerous standstill.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nAnd it has been claimed that they have stolen more than $ 1bn in an international crime spree.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nThey are the Lazarus Group, a shadowy cabal of hackers accused of working on behalf of the North Korean state.\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\nFrom the streets of Dhaka to the casinos of Macau to the secretive capital of Pyongyang, this shocking story uncovers the secret world of the Lazarus Group, their victims and those who have tried - and so far, failed - to stop them. \u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e'Madly intriguing'\u003c/b\u003e\u003ci\u003e Guardian\u003c/i\u003e","sequence":1,"textSource":null,"textAuthor":null}]}},"affiliateLinks":[{"affiliateTypeId":1,"affiliateType":"amazon","affiliateDisplay":"Amazon","url":"https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/product/0241554276?tag=prhmarketing2552-21"},{"affiliateTypeId":4,"affiliateType":"blackwells","affiliateDisplay":"Blackwells","url":"https://blackwells.co.uk/bookshop/product/9780241554272?a_aid=prh"},{"affiliateTypeId":5,"affiliateType":"bookshop.org","affiliateDisplay":"Bookshop.org","url":"https://uk.bookshop.org/a/447/9780241554272?utm=penguinbookpage"},{"affiliateTypeId":6,"affiliateType":"foyles","affiliateDisplay":"Foyles","url":"https://www.foyles.co.uk/book/9780241554272"},{"affiliateTypeId":8,"affiliateType":"hive","affiliateDisplay":"Hive","url":"https://track.webgains.com/click.html?wgcampaignid=1304995\u0026wgprogramid=10671\u0026clickref=book-page\u0026wgtarget=http://www.hive.co.uk/Search?keyword=9780241554272"},{"affiliateTypeId":12,"affiliateType":"waterstones","affiliateDisplay":"Waterstones","url":"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=3787\u0026awinaffid=117976\u0026clickref=penguin-book-page\u0026p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.waterstones.com%2Fbook%2F9780241554272"},{"affiliateTypeId":13,"affiliateType":"tgjones","affiliateDisplay":"TGJones","url":"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=3017\u0026awinaffid=117976\u0026clickref=penguin-book-page\u0026ued=https://www.tgjonesonline.co.uk/Search/Keyword?keyword=9780241554272"}],"safetyMarks":[],"safetyLabels":[],"flags":["SEE_INSIDE"],"moreFromThisAuthor":{"works":[],"count":null,"workListUrl":null},"moreInThisSeries":{"works":[],"count":null,"workListUrl":null},"categories":[{"catId":2040541188,"catDesc":"Business \u0026 Management","catUri":"200301","menuText":"Business \u0026 Management","leafNode":true,"deepestNode":true,"seq":1},{"catId":2040541192,"catDesc":"Computing \u0026 Information Technology","catUri":"200401","menuText":"Computing \u0